Detailed Description

Reply to a CoveredIDsRequestPacket.

After the normal header this request packet contains: {tabular}{lll} { Pos} & { Size}& { Destription} \ REPLY_HEADER_SIZE & 4 bytes & mapID, is MAX_UINT32 if packet contains MapIDs \ +4 & 4 bytes & number IDs (stored as length of packet)\ for each ID & 4 bytes & ID \ {tabular}
